-- IDIM Dental Clinic (Instituto De IMplantología) - English-speaking dental clinic in Valencia
('IDIM Dental Clinic', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Valencia with over 30 years of experience. IDIM (Instituto De IMplantología) is a multidisciplinary team of specialized dentists led by Dr. Miguel Peñarrocha and Dr. David Peñarrocha, both experts in oral surgery, implantology and oral rehabilitation. Dr. David Peñarrocha studied at the British school Caxton College and holds a Cambridge C2 Proficiency in English with grade A, ensuring perfect communication with English-speaking patients. The clinic specializes in dental implants (including immediate loading, All-On-4, zygomatic and pterygoid implants for complex cases), oral surgery (wisdom teeth extraction, cyst treatment, apicoectomy, gum grafts, bone grafts), and aesthetics and oral rehabilitation (veneers, crowns, bridges, Invisalign orthodontics, teeth whitening, fillings, endodontics). They offer intravenous conscious sedation for anxious patients or complex procedures. The clinic is equipped with state-of-the-art technology and focuses on minimally invasive procedures. Located near Alameda and Colón metro stations. Bus lines 1, 4, 10, 25, 47, and 95 serve the area.', 'Plaza América, 5, 46004 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 344 675', 'america@idim.es', 'https://idim.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
